title: What's In a Name?
description:
Welcome to episode 130 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! This episode I gently discuss the impact names have on people. There is no cohesive story to tell, just an assortment of random thoughts that will keep you distracted and disoriented. Enjoy!

Visit our website: www.SleepandRelaxASMR.com to get updates and access to special promos on awesome brands!
